headline.main: NEW BLOW DEALT AXIS LIBYAN ARMY; Rommel Attacks Again to Halt Envelopment, But British Report Damage Inflicted

lead_paragraph: CAIRO, Egypt, Dec. 31 (AP) -- British tanks and planes, hacking away at the remnants of German General Erwin Rommel's Libyan army, were reported tonight to be closing in for the kill at Agedabia.
abstract: RAF bombs Axis convoys along coastal road to Tripoli
